Specify location of .DEFAULT.vgf in a table (hpc/opc)

The location of the Product Generation work file, .DEFAULT.vgf, may
now be specified by the user. The entry "WORK_FILE_DIR" in prefs.tbl
is the path to the directory to be used for the work file. The default
value as delivered is the current directory, ".". This value of this
preference may be any directory for which the user has write 
permission. The value may include an environment variable. 

